Me and You and Everyone We Know;;84;;82;;R;;Single dad Richard (John Hawkes) meets Christine (Miranda July), a starving artist who moonlights as a cabbie. They awkwardly attempt to start a romance, but Richard's divorce has left him emotionally damaged, and he struggles to remain open to the possibilities of this new relationship. Meanwhile, Richard's sons, the adolescent Peter (Miles Thompson) and 6-year-old Robby (Brandon Ratcliff), take part in their own clumsy experiments with the opposite sex.;;Drama,Comedy;;Miranda July;;2005;;John Hawkes,Miranda July,Miles Thompson,Brandon Ratcliff,Carlie Westerman,Natasha Slayton,Najarra Townsend;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/me_and_you_and_everyone_we_know